@startuml ZMQ_RPC_Metrics_0_8_1
title ZMQ RPC 分段指标 (0.8.1) — MetaPb.ticks + 直方图 µs

participant Client as "Client 线程\n(Python / KVClient / Stub)"
participant StubOrUnary as "Stub / Unary\n(zmq_stub_impl / unary_client)"
participant FrontQ as "ZmqFrontend\nSendMsg + 路由"
participant Server as "ZmqService\n(FrontendToBackend,\nServiceToClient)"
participant WorkerQ as "WorkerEntry\n(队列 worker)"
participant WorkerD as "WorkerEntryWithoutMsgQ\n(DirectExec)"
participant Agent as "WorkAgent\n(独占连接回包)"
participant Meta as "MetaPb.ticks\n(墙钟 ns)"

legend right
|= Color |= Meaning |
|<#C8E6C9> Green|墙钟 tick：`RecordTick` → `TickPb.ts` = `GetTimeSinceEpoch()` (ns)|
|<#E1F5FE> Blue|服务端回包前统一写 SERVER_SEND + 三段 server 直方图|
|<#FFF9C4> Yellow|客户端收包后 `RecordRpcLatencyMetrics`（7 指标里 4 个在 client 进程）|
endlegend

== Request ==

Client -> StubOrUnary: RPC / unary send
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(CLIENT_ENQUEUE)
StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Meta: (async/unary) RecordTick(CLIENT_TO_STUB)\nRecordTick(CLIENT_SEND) 等
StubOrUnary -> FrontQ: SendMsg / mQue_->SendMsg
FrontQ -> Server: MetaPb + payload（ticks 随 meta 传递）

== Server 收包 ==

Server -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(SERVER_RECV)\n`FrontendToBackend` 解析后

alt 常规队列 worker（非 DirectExec）
    Server -> WorkerQ: dispatch
    WorkerQ -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(SERVER_DEQUEUE)
    WorkerQ -[#2E7D32]> WorkerQ: business
    WorkerQ -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(SERVER_EXEC_END)
else DirectExecInternalMethod（独占 / 部分内连路径）
    Server -> WorkerD: DirectCallMethod
    WorkerD -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(SERVER_DEQUEUE)\n（与 WorkerEntry 对齐）
    WorkerD -[#2E7D32]> WorkerD: business
    WorkerD -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(SERVER_EXEC_END)
end

== Server 回包前（直方图 + 派生 tick）==

note over Server, Meta
**`ZmqRecordServerSendLatencyMetrics(meta)`**（`zmq_service.cpp`）\n
1) `RecordTick(SERVER_SEND)` 墙钟\n
2) **`RecordServerLatencyMetrics`**：\n
   - `zmq_server_*`：`Observe(ZmqDurationNsToMetricUs(Δns))`\n
   - 取 **同名 tick 最后一次** ts（`FindLastTickTs`）\n
   - **守卫**：缺 `SERVER_RECV` / `EXEC_END` 时不做无意义差分；\n
     **禁止**在 `SERVER_EXEC_END==0` 时用 `SERVER_SEND−0` 写 reply（避免直方图污染）\n
3) 追加 **`SERVER_EXEC_NS`**：`ts = (SERVER_EXEC_END − SERVER_RECV)` **时长 ns**（非墙钟），供 client 算 **rpc_network**
end note

Server -[#2196F3]> Meta: ZmqRecordServerSendLatencyMetrics(meta)

alt 经 ZmqService::ServiceToClient（队列 / IO 回包）
    Server -[#2196F3]> FrontQ: reply MetaPb + frames
else 经 WorkAgent::ServiceToClient（独占直连）
    Server -> Agent: outMsg
    Agent -[#2196F3]> Meta: **同上** ZmqRecordServerSendLatencyMetrics(meta)\n（与 ServiceToClient 共用实现）
    Agent -> Client: encode + send
end

== Client 收包 ==

StubOrUnary -[#2E7D32]> Meta: RecordTick(CLIENT_RECV)
StubOrUnary -[#F9A825]> StubOrUnary: **RecordRpcLatencyMetrics(meta)**\n（`zmq_stub_impl.h`）\n
• CLIENT_QUEUING / STUB_SEND\n
• E2E = CLIENT_RECV − CLIENT_ENQUEUE\n
• NETWORK = E2E − **FindTickTs(SERVER_EXEC_NS)**\n
（`SERVER_EXEC_NS.ts` 为 **duration ns**）

note right of Meta
**单位**：墙钟 tick 的 `ts` 均为 **ns**；写入 `kv_metrics` 的 7 段直方图统一 **`ZmqDurationNsToMetricUs`** → **µs**。\n
**`SERVER_EXEC_NS`**：不得与链上其它墙钟 tick 做「相邻相减」当 lap；仅作 **duration 字段** 或 E2E 分解。\n
验收：worker glog 中 **`[ZmqTickOrder]`** + `metrics_summary` JSON；详见 README / test-walkthrough。
end note

note over StubOrUnary
7 个 Histogram 名（`kv_metrics`）：\n
zmq_client_queuing_latency, zmq_client_stub_send_latency,\n
zmq_server_queue_wait_latency, zmq_server_exec_latency, zmq_server_reply_latency,\n
zmq_rpc_e2e_latency, zmq_rpc_network_latency
end note

@enduml
